{"tid":1590791,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我地係咪要擺爭取雙普選做主菜？","createTime":"2019-09-24T01:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T02:03:03.000Z","uid":158662,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e07f69268c6b68b016bc931818b3f58982258b6b","tid":1590791,"uid":158662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:45:16.000Z","msg":"無錯 狗暴問題好撚想追究佢地<br />\n要佢地血債血償<br />\n但問題係睇番法國黃背心<br />\n佢地就係將焦點轉左去警暴問題<br />\n無左對準政權<br />\n令到而家黃背心搞到咁<br />\n我諗 我地使唔使煲大雙普選呢個point<br />\n令到成個運動有一個對準政權既焦點<br />\n當然 班狗係一撚定要清算<br />\n純討論下"},{"pid":"073a11ce67d6982ae3a1ba1de6d4647f7ad5890f","tid":1590791,"uid":158662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:45:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80ce1a1209750f88e0bf4452fe9888cf198509a9","tid":1590791,"uid":158662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:45:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"96e3fed86d2d5e90dd4fc2506e9e063b2b6b5bc9","tid":1590791,"uid":158662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:45:56.000Z","msg":"再自推一下"},{"pid":"dc03f908d67414c23df0370f95490c25991c20e7","tid":1590791,"uid":158662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:46:14.000Z","msg":"再黎推多一下"},{"pid":"1488bf2211454521429fd98df1e9eace0b23547d","tid":1590791,"uid":152455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:46:32.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1555ef61522c03bea447fb640e3b8af3b18d7b","tid":1590791,"uid":158662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:46:50.000Z","msg":"純論下 真係唔想就咁輸"},{"pid":"b6a59d289780a555758d5d5e8411034e0995b2e2","tid":1590791,"uid":158662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:47:50.000Z","msg":"可能文宣要多d呢個方向 我見文宣都係狗暴 但比較少見到真雙普選"},{"pid":"22a027e7cc8f5be10d61dbef16aff577016b71a5","tid":1590791,"uid":32505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"927新屋嶺<br />\n929大遊行"},{"pid":"99a9b3df0f09be340535130f5637c75d3d55c6e6","tid":1590791,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:48:40.000Z","msg":"政制唔改，香港冇未來<br />\n亦唔會清算到班狗"},{"pid":"44e13c51d3e74d28980c7a4903472cff23486ae5","tid":1590791,"uid":158662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"d04ea0f1916bd9911fa310cd3efe82171b268c66","tid":1590791,"uid":158662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99a9b3df0f09be340535130f5637c75d3d55c6e6","tid":1590791,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:48:40.000Z","msg":"政制唔改，香港冇未來<br />\n亦唔會清算到班狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:49:19.000Z","msg":"岩呀 所以我就覺得要對準番個政權"},{"pid":"9064f404baebeea53d0f11aedc4b77f256874d43","tid":1590791,"uid":213010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:50:08.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"b985e57c9b41f25661c56fc79c4dbdfee5ce729b","tid":1590791,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=5be4f93b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外就係<br />\n過去個兩個月正正常常係比應屆DSE同學仔溫書休息既<br />\n可惜呢個政府搞到大家奉獻左成個暑假，為左自己又好，為左將來又好，為左下一代又好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前有見連登上有多個關於網上問功課谷既需求，有見及此就有呢個DSE支援服務。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，免費網上問功課谷一直以唔張揚嘅方法存在。谷內有十多位Tutors (當中包括現職老師及名校畢業生在讀生)同DSE同學仔。形式係以分科細谷你問我答為主，亦有提供簡單練習同改文服務。同學亦可以問升學選科等問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直隱姓埋名係為左保障學生安全。但見到需求增加，又多左好多不同既補習post。所以我地希望提供俾同學多一個安全安心既選擇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如有同學有需要，請聯絡：<br />\nTG: mama612<br />\n(暫時有足夠Tutor所以暫不接受更多tutor)<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}